sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant C as Client
    participant MC as MetricsController
    participant MS as MetricsService
    participant MR as MetricsRepository
    participant DB as Database

    Note over C,DB: 1 · Ranking de atletas por km — RF035 · RN10

    C->>+MC: GET /metrics/events/{eventId}/athletes
    Note over MC: requireAuth — JWT obrigatório
    MC->>+MS: getAthleteKm(eventId)
    MS->>+MR: athleteKmByEvent(eventId)
    MR->>+DB: SELECT athletes, SUM(distance) as total_km<br/>FROM checkpoints JOIN shifts JOIN athletes<br/>WHERE event_id = $1 AND shifts.status = 'finished'<br/>GROUP BY athlete_id ORDER BY total_km DESC
    DB-->>-MR: athlete ranking rows[]
    MR-->>-MS: athletes[]
    MS-->>-MC: athletes[]
    MC-->>-C: 200 [ { id, name, team_name, total_km, shift_count } ]

    Note over C,DB: 2 · Histórico de turnos de um atleta — RF036 · RN10

    C->>+MC: GET /metrics/athletes/{athleteId}/shifts
    MC->>+MS: getAvgDistancePerShift(athleteId)
    MS->>+MR: shiftsByAthlete(athleteId)
    MR->>+DB: SELECT shifts, distance, duration, speed<br/>FROM shifts WHERE athlete_id = $1<br/>ORDER BY started_at DESC
    DB-->>-MR: shift rows[]
    MR-->>-MS: { shifts[], avg_distance }
    MS-->>-MC: result
    MC-->>-C: 200 { shifts: [ { id, distance, duration, avg_speed, started_at } ], avg_distance }

    Note over C,DB: 3 · Snapshots de km ao longo do evento — RF037 · RN10

    C->>+MC: GET /metrics/athletes/{athleteId}/snapshots?event_id={id}
    MC->>+MS: getKmSnapshots(athleteId, eventId)
    MS->>+MR: kmSnapshotsByAthlete(athleteId, eventId)
    MR->>+DB: SELECT SUM(distance) acumulado por hora<br/>FROM checkpoints JOIN shifts<br/>WHERE athlete_id = $1 AND event_id = $2
    DB-->>-MR: snapshot rows[]
    MR-->>-MS: snapshots[]
    MS-->>-MC: snapshots[]
    MC-->>-C: 200 [ { hour, cumulative_km } ]

    Note over C,DB: 4 · Desempenho individual do atleta — RF049 · RF052

    C->>+MC: GET /metrics/athletes/{athleteId}/performance
    Note over MC: requireAuth — JWT obrigatório
    MC->>+MS: getAthletePerformance(athleteId)
    MS->>+MR: performanceByAthlete(athleteId)
    MR->>+DB: SELECT total_km, total_shifts, avg_speed,<br/>best_shift_km, team_name<br/>FROM shifts JOIN checkpoints JOIN teams
    DB-->>-MR: performance row
    MR-->>-MS: performanceData
    MS-->>-MC: performanceData
    MC-->>-C: 200 { total_km, total_shifts, avg_speed, best_shift_km, team_name }

    Note over C,DB: 5 · Link público de compartilhamento — RF050 · RN36 (sem autenticação)

    C->>+MC: GET /metrics/athletes/{athleteId}/share
    Note over MC: Rota pública — NÃO requer requireAuth (declarada antes do router.use(requireAuth))
    MC->>+MS: shareAthletePerformance(athleteId)
    MS->>+MR: performanceByAthlete(athleteId)
    MR->>+DB: SELECT desempenho público do atleta
    DB-->>-MR: performanceData
    MR-->>-MS: performanceData
    MS-->>-MC: performanceData
    MC-->>-C: 200 { name, team, total_km, avg_speed, total_shifts } (sem dados sensíveis)

    Note over C,DB: 6 · Atleta não encontrado

    C->>+MC: GET /metrics/athletes/999/performance
    MC->>+MS: getAthletePerformance(999)
    MS->>+MR: performanceByAthlete(999)
    MR->>+DB: SELECT ... WHERE athlete_id = 999
    DB-->>-MR: null
    MR-->>-MS: null
    MS-->>-MC: null
    MC-->>-C: 404 { error: "Atleta não encontrado" }
